# Survey Form Project

This is a simple **Survey Form** built as part of the [freeCodeCamp Responsive Web Design Certification](https://www.freecodecamp.org/).  
It was created to practice **HTML5** and **CSS3** fundamentals such as forms, inputs, labels, and responsive layouts.

## 🚀 Live Demo
👉 [View Survey Form](https://jj879304.github.io/survey-form/)  

## 🛠️ Built With
- HTML5  
- CSS3 (Flexbox, Responsive Design)  

## 🎯 Features
- User-friendly form layout  
- Required and optional fields  
- Responsive design (works on mobile & desktop)  

## 📖 Lessons Learned
- How to structure a form with `input`, `textarea`, `select`, and `radio/checkbox`.  
- Importance of labels and accessibility.  
- How to style forms cleanly with CSS.  

